<p><span class="anchor" id="p55"></span>بَهْزًا ضربه فِي صَدره وَدفعه دفعا عنيفا ونحاه<a href="#p55" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span><span class="c2">(أبهزه)</span> بهزه<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span><span class="c2">(باهزه)</span> الشَّيْء سبقه إِلَيْهِ<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
